title: Looks Like The Teen Mom 2 Cast Is Getting A New Addition!
text:
Teen Mom 2 is about to get a lot more exciting!
It's being reported the hit MTV show's cast is growing as Briana DeJesus and her baby bump are rumored to be joining season eight!
According to The Ashley's Reality Roundup , the 22-year-old will be joining Jenelle Evans, Kailyn Lowry , Leah Messer , and Chelsea Houska for what we can only imagine is more drama.
Related: Teen Mom 2 's Javi Marroquin Is Dating THIS MTV Reality TV Star 
In case you didn't know, the preggers reality TV star last starred on Teen Mom 3 back in 2013, and just this January she announced she was expecting her second child!
It's said Briana has already started filming for the upcoming season, but the rumors have yet to be confirmed by her or MTV!
So inneresting!
Would U be interested in seeing the Florida native on the show??
